The Zoning Resolution of the City of New York, effective as of December 15, 1961, and as subsequently amended, is further amended by changing the Zoning Map, Section No. 28d: by establishing within an existing R6 District a C2-4 District bounded by West Brighton Avenue, West 2nd Street, Sea Breeze Avenue, and West 5th Street a line 250 feet westerly of West 2nd Street, Borough of Brooklyn, Community District 13, as shown on a diagram (for illustrative purposes only) date September 23, 2019, and subject to the conditions of CEQR Declaration E-535. 

Adopted.

